\c 35
\s Kuteerera kweVaRekabhi
\p
\v 1 Shoko rakasvika kuna Jeremiya kubva kuna Jehovha pamazuva aJehoyakimu mwanakomana waJosiya mambo waJudha, richiti:
\v 2 Enda kuimba yeVaRekabhi ugotaura kwavari, uye uuye navo kuimba yaJehovha, mune rimwe remakamuri, ugovapa waini kuti vanwe.
\v 3 Zvino ndakatora Jaazania mwanakomana waJeremiya, mwanakomana waHabhazania, nehama dzake, nevanakomana vake vese, neimba yese yeVaRekabhi.
\v 4 Zvino ndakauya navo muimba yaJehovha, mukamuri revanakomana vaHanani mwanakomana waIghidhari, munhu waMwari, yaiva pedo pakamuri remachinda, raiva pamusoro pekamuri raMaaseia mwanakomana waSharumi, mutariri wechikumbaridzo.
\v 5 Zvino ndakaisa pamberi pevanakomana veimba yeVaRekabhi mbiya dzizere newaini, nemikombe, ndokuti kwavari: Inwai waini.
\v 6 Asi vakati: Hatinwi waini, nokuti Jonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi baba vedu wakatiraira achiti: Musanwa waini, imwi nevanakomana venyu kusvika rinhi narinhi.
\v 7 Uye musavaka imba, musadzvara mbeu, musasima munda wemizambiringa, musava nazvo, asi mazuva enyu ese muchagara mumatende, kuti murarame mazuva mazhinji munyika yamuri vatorwa.
\v 8 Naizvozvo takateerera inzwi raJonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi baba vedu, pane zvese zvaakatiraira, kuti tisanwa waini mazuva edu ese, isu nevakadzi vedu, vanakomana vedu uye vanasikana vedu;
\v 9 uye kuti tisazvivakira dzimba dzekugara, uye kuti tisava nemunda wemizambiringa, kana munda, kana mbeu;
\v 10 asi takagara mumatende, ndokuteerera, uye takaita zvinoenderana nezveseJonadhabhi baba vedu zvavakatiraira.
\v 11 Asi zvakaitika Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi paakakwira panyika, kuti takati: uyai, zvino ngatiende kuJerusarema nokuda kwekutya hondo yeVaKaradhiya, uye nekuda kwekutya hondo yeVaSiriya; naizvozvo tigere paJerusarema.
\p
\v 12 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Jeremiya richiti:
\v 13 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo, Enda unoudza varume Mwari waIsraeri: Enda unoudza varume vaJudha nevagari veJerusarema, \add uti\add*: Hamugamuciritendi kurangwa, kuti muteerere mashoko angu here? Ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 14 Mashoko aJonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi, aakaraira vanakomana vake, kuti varege kunwa waini, anoteererwa; kusvikira zuva ranhasi havamwi, nokuti vanoteerera murairo wababa wavo. Asi ini ndakataura nemi, ndichimuka mangwanani ndichitaura; asi hamuna kunditeerera.
\v 15 Ndakatumawo kwamuri varanda vangu vese vavaporofita, ndichimuka mangwanani, ndichivatuma, ndichiti: Dzokai zvino umwe neumwe panzira yake yakaipa, munatse zvamunoita, murege kutevera vamwe vamwari muchivashumira, ipapo muchagara panyika yandakakupai imwi namadzibaba enyu; asi hamuna kurerekera nzeve dzenyu, kana kunditeerera.
\v 16 Vanakomana vaJonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi vakateerera murairo wababa wavo, waakavaraira, asi vanhu ava havana kunditeerera;
\v 17 naizvozvo zvanzi naJehovha, Mwari wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Tarirai, ndichauisa pamusoro paJudha napamusoro pavese vagere Jerusarema zvakaipa zvese zvandakareva pamusoro pavo; nokuti ndakataura navo, asi havana kunzwa, ndakavadana, asi havana kudavira.
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jeremiya akati kuimba yavaRekabhi: Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Zvamakateerera murairo waJonadhabhi baba venyu, mukachengeta zviga zvavo zvese, mukaita zvese sezvamakarairwa navo;
\v 19 naizvozvo zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, iye Mwari waIsraeri: Jonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi haangashaiwi munhu ungamira pamberi pangu nokusingaperi.